---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Soluciones para PYMES y Emprendedores — SkyBrandMX">
    <main>
        <!-- HERO PYMES -->
        <section class="relative pt-40 pb-20 overflow-hidden bg-[#081014]">
            <div class="absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/10 to-transparent"></div>
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 text-center relative z-10">
                <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#FF6B00]/10 border border-[#FF6B00]/20 text-[#FF6B00] text-xs font-black mb-8">
                    Startups y PYMES
                </div>
                <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black text-white tracking-tighter mb-8 leading-none">
                    Lanza y centraliza <br/><span class="text-[#70D1C6]">tu negocio digital.</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="text-xl text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-bold mb-12">
                    Deja de pagar 5 herramientas distintas. Gestiona tus ventas, envíos y clientes desde un panel unificado diseñado para llevarte al siguiente nivel.
                </p>
                
                <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 mb-20">
                    <a href="#planes-pyme" class="px-8 py-4 bg-[#FF6B00] text-white rounded-2xl text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(255,107,0,0.3)]">Ver Planes PYME</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- COMO FUNCIONA PARA PYMES -->
        <section class="py-24 bg-white">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
                <div class="text-center mb-20">
                    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-[#105971] tracking-tighter mb-4">
                        El motor de crecimiento para tu empresa
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 font-bold max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg">
                        Te damos infraestructura de nivel Enterprise a una fracción del costo.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                    <!-- Feature 1 -->
                    <div class="p-8 bg-[#F8FAFC] rounded-[2.5rem] border border-slate-100 hover:border-[#70D1C6]/30 transition-all">
                        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-[#105971]/5 flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mb-8">🌐</div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-[#105971] mb-4">Todo en Uno</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 font-bold leading-relaxed text-sm">Desde el diseño de tu tienda online hasta el CRM. Elimina la necesidad de conectar zapiers o plugins complejos.</p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Feature 2 -->
                    <div class="p-8 bg-[#F8FAFC] rounded-[2.5rem] border border-slate-100 hover:border-[#70D1C6]/30 transition-all">
                        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-[#105971]/5 flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mb-8">📦</div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-[#105971] mb-4">Logística Sencilla</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 font-bold leading-relaxed text-sm">Tarifas preferenciales de FedEx, DHL y Estafeta. Genera guías en lote sin copiar y pegar datos de tus clientes.</p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Feature 3 -->
                    <div class="p-8 bg-[#F8FAFC] rounded-[2.5rem] border border-slate-100 hover:border-[#70D1C6]/30 transition-all">
                        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-[#105971]/5 flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mb-8">🧾</div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-[#105971] mb-4">Facturación Automática</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 font-bold leading-relaxed text-sm">Cumple con el SAT sin sufrir. Timbrado 4.0 automático cuando tu cliente completa una compra.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- PRICING DEDICADO A PYMES -->
        <section id="planes-pyme" class="py-24 bg-[#F8FAFC] border-t border-slate-100">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
                <div class="text-center mb-16">
                    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black tracking-tighter mb-4 text-[#105971]">
                        Planes claros para tu etapa
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 font-bold text-lg">Cancela cuando quieras, sin contratos forzosos.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-center max-w-6xl mx-auto">
                    <!-- Plan Creador -->
                    <div class="p-10 bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-sm flex flex-col hover:shadow-xl transition-all h-full">
                        <div class="mb-8">
                            <h5 class="text-xl font-black text-[#105971] mb-2">Plan Creador</h5>
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 font-bold leading-relaxed mb-6">Lanza tu primer ecosistema digital.</p>
                            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-1">
                                <span class="text-4xl font-black text-[#105971]">$2,500</span>
                                <span class="text-slate-500 font-bold">MXN/mes</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-10 flex-1">
                            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm font-bold text-slate-600">
                                <span class="text-[#70D1C6] text-lg font-black italic">✔️</span> Diseño Web Premium + Hosting
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm font-bold text-slate-600">
                                <span class="text-[#70D1C6] text-lg font-black italic">✔️</span> CRM (3 Usuarios)
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm font-bold text-slate-600">
                                <span class="text-[#70D1C6] text-lg font-black italic">✔️</span> 100 Guías de envío/mes
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                        <a href="https://web.whatsapp.com/send?phone=5525582310" class="w-full text-center px-6 py-4 border-2 border-[#105971] text-[#105971] rounded-2xl text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-[#105971] hover:text-white transition-all">Empezar Ahora</a>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Plan Evolucion -->
                    <div class="p-10 bg-white border-2 border-[#FF6B00] rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-[0_25px_60px_-15px_rgba(255,107,0,0.15)] flex flex-col relative scale-[1.02] z-10 hover:scale-105 transition-all h-full">
                        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-[#FF6B00] text-white text-[10px] font-black px-4 py-2 rounded-bl-2xl uppercase tracking-widest">Favorito</div>
                        <div class="mb-8">
                            <h5 class="text-xl font-black text-[#105971] mb-2">Plan Evolución</h5>
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 font-bold leading-relaxed mb-6">Automatización y rediseño web.</p>
                            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2">
                                <span class="text-5xl font-black text-[#105971]">$4,500</span>
                                <span class="text-slate-500 font-bold">MXN/mes</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-10 flex-1">
                            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm font-black text-[#105971]">
                                <span class="text-[#FF6B00] text-lg font-black italic">✔️</span> Guías masivas (1 clic)
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm font-black text-[#105971]">
                                <span class="text-[#FF6B00] text-lg font-black italic">✔️</span> Facturación SAT 4.0 ilimitada
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm font-black text-[#105971]">
                                <span class="text-[#FF6B00] text-lg font-black italic">✔️</span> Ads Meta/Google con IA
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm font-black text-[#105971]">
                                <span class="text-[#FF6B00] text-lg font-black italic">✔️</span> Soporte Priority WhatsApp
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                        <a href="https://web.whatsapp.com/send?phone=5525582310" class="w-full text-center px-6 py-4 bg-[#FF6B00] text-white rounded-2xl text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-[#E66000] transition-all shadow-xl shadow-orange-200">Impulsar Ahora</a>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Plan Plug & Play -->
                    <div class="p-10 bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-sm flex flex-col hover:shadow-xl transition-all h-full">
                        <div class="mb-8">
                            <h5 class="text-xl font-black text-[#105971] mb-2">Plug & Play</h5>
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 font-bold leading-relaxed mb-6">Conecta tu web actual a SkyBrandMX.</p>
                            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-1">
                                <span class="text-4xl font-black text-[#105971]">$1,500</span>
                                <span class="text-slate-500 font-bold">MXN/mes</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-10 flex-1">
                            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm font-bold text-slate-600">
                                <span class="text-[#70D1C6] text-lg font-black italic">✔️</span> Integración Shopify/WooCommerce
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm font-bold text-slate-600">
                                <span class="text-[#70D1C6] text-lg font-black italic">✔️</span> Email & SMS Automáticos
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm font-bold text-slate-600">
                                <span class="text-[#70D1C6] text-lg font-black italic">✔️</span> Todo el panel logístico y SAT
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                        <a href="https://web.whatsapp.com/send?phone=5525582310" class="w-full text-center px-6 py-4 border-2 border-[#105971] text-[#105971] rounded-2xl text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-[#105971] hover:text-white transition-all">Activar Acceso</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>
